<p>What does it take to focus on clean-up work for 3 months? What I learned is:</p>

<ul>
  <li>clean-up work is a non-destructive way to indulge in <a href="http://sethgodin.typepad.com/seths_blog/2005/03/dont_shave_that.html">yak shaving</a>; oh sure, you start all high-minded, ready to whip <code class="highlighter-rouge">this-terrible-stylesheet.css</code> into shape and a week later youâ€™ve produced 6 pull requests, deleted a thousand lines of code, and feel pretty awesome. But you still havenâ€™t deleted the file. (Yet.)</li>
