  <li>you absolutely need the support of your team and your team lead/manager/boss. We are a pull request kind of organization and it was not uncommon for me to open 5 in a week. If your team doesnâ€™t respond well to a steady flow of pull requests: you in danger, girl.</li>
</ul>

